title: Introducing Bachelor Happy Hour with Rachel & Ali
description:
“Bachelor Happy Hour with Rachel & Ali” takes fans behind the scenes with all things Bachelor Nation-related in the first ever, official Bachelor podcast. You’ll hear from current cast members and get the details on what really happened when the cameras stopped rolling.

 Start listening now at: http://wondery.fm/BHHAB
